    2000. This means that in order to either buy or sell shares of the Company, a
    shareholder would have to open a demat account and get the existing physical
    shares converted into demat mode for selling the shares. Also those who intend
    to buy the Company's shares through stock market would necessarily have to open
    a demat account.
